.container#interactive-content
  #incorrect.modal.fade aria-hidden="true" role="dialog"
    .modal-dialog
      .modal-content
        .modal-body
          | Invalid entry. Please try again.
        .modal-footer
          button.btn.btn-danger.try-again data-dismiss="modal" Try again

  .row.justify-content-center.main-text
    .col-12.text-center.info-text
      p Rate the attractiveness of these 10 celebrities on a scale from 1 to 10.
    .col-12.stage-1.stage.art.text-center
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/angelina-jolie.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 Angelina Jolie
    .col-12.stage-2.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/ben-affleck.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 Ben Affleck
    .col-12.stage-3.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/beyonce-knowles.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 Beyoncé Knowles
    .col-12.stage-4.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/brad-pitt.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 Brad Pitt
    .col-12.stage-5.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/george-clooney.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 George Clooney
    .col-12.stage-6.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/john-mayer.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 John Mayer
    .col-12.stage-7.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/kate-upton.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 Kate Upton
    .col-12.stage-8.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/lena-dunham.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 Lena Dunham
    .col-12.stage-9.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/miley-cyrus.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 Miley Cyrus
    .col-12.stage-10.stage.art.text-center.d-none
      = image_tag image_url('facial-symmetry/ryan-gosling.jpg'), class: 'img-fluid celebrity', alt: ''
      h2.mt-2 Ryan Gosling
    .col-12.stage-11.stage.d-none
      p One of the most important predictors of attractiveness is facial symmetry, meaning how similar the two halves of a face are. Each of the celebrities whose attractiveness you rated has had their facial symmetry calculated. Select “Next” to see how your attractiveness ratings correspond to their facial symmetry.
