    .col-12.text-center
      p How did your ratings match up to the facial symmetry measures?
    .col-12.col-md-6.d-flex.justify-content-center.text-center
      p.sr-only
        |Angelina Jolie received a facial symmetry score of 7.13. You rated her attractiveness as 
        span.angelina-jolie-user
      p.sr-only
        |Ben Affleck received a facial symmetry score of 6.55. You rated his attractiveness as 
        span.ben-affleck-user
      p.sr-only
